%% ====================================================================
%% 2. SYSTEM FLOWCHART
%% ====================================================================

flowchart TD
  title 2. System Flowchart - End-to-End Flow

  S([VISIT]) --> A[Public Pages<br/>/, /criteria, /docs, /developer]
  A --> B{Register?}
  B -->|Yes| C[Register Form<br/>POST /api/register]
  C --> D{Login?}
  B -->|No| D
  D -->|Not yet| A
  D -->|Yes| E[Credentials Login<br/>POST /api/auth/...nextauth]
  E --> F{bcrypt valid?}
  F -->|No| G[LOGIN_FAILED audit]
  G --> D
  F -->|Yes| H[JWT Token issued<br/>id + role embedded]
  H --> I{Middleware proxy.ts<br/>check role}
  I -->|role = admin| J[Admin Dashboard<br/>redirect /admin/dashboard]
  I -->|role = analyst| K[Analyst Compare<br/>redirect /analyst/compare]
  J --> L[Admin features:<br/>Analytics, Providers,<br/>Weights, Users, Audit]
  K --> M[Analyst features:<br/>Dashboard, Compare,<br/>History, Profile]
  M --> N{MOORA Compare?}
  N -->|Yes| O[3-Step Wizard:<br/>1. Select Providers<br/>2. Input Fuzzy Scores<br/>3. POST /api/comparisons]
  O --> P[computeMoora()<br/>Normalization → Weight → Yi → Rank]
  P --> Q[Save to DB<br/>+ Audit Log]
  Q --> N
  N -->|No| R([END])


