  SH --> USERS[👥 Users<br/>/admin/users]

  USERS --> U1[List all analysts<br/>prisma.user.findMany]
  USERS --> U2[Stats: total users, avg comps,<br/>most active]
  USERS --> U3[User Detail /admin/users/:id<br/>profile + full comparison history]

  SH --> AUDIT[📋 Audit Trail<br/>/admin/audit]

  AUDIT --> AU1[Last 50 entries<br/>prisma.auditLog.findMany take:50]
  AUDIT --> AU2[Columns: Waktu, User,<br/>Aksi, Entitas, Detail]
