%% ====================================================================
%% 5. MOORA CALCULATION FLOWCHART
%% ====================================================================

flowchart TD
  title 5. MOORA Calculation Flowchart

  S([START: User submits comparison<br/>POST /api/comparisons]) --> INPUT[📥 INPUT]

  INPUT --> I1[providerInputs[]:<br/>selected provider IDs<br/>+ fuzzy scores 1/3/5<br/>per criterion]
  INPUT --> I2[Fetch providers from DB<br/>prisma.provider.findMany]
  INPUT --> I3[Fetch criteria + weights<br/>prisma.criterion.findMany]

  I1 --> M1[📊 STEP 1: BUILD DECISION MATRIX]
  I2 --> M1
  I3 --> M1

  M1 --> M1a[Extract raw values<br/>per provider per criterion]
  M1 --> M1b[Label columns:<br/>benefit = + , cost = -]

  M1a --> M2[📐 STEP 2: VECTOR NORMALIZATION]
  M1b --> M2

  M2 --> M2a[For each criterion column j:<br/>sqrt_sum = √(Σ xij²)]
  M2 --> M2b[Nij = xij / sqrt_sum<br/>Result: normalized matrix<br/>all values in [0, 1]]

  M2a --> M3[⚖️ STEP 3: APPLY WEIGHTS]
  M2b --> M3

  M3 --> M3a[For each cell:<br/>Vij = Nij × Wj]
  M3 --> M3b[Wj from admin config<br/>Σ Wj = 1.00 (100%)]

  M3a --> M4[🔢 STEP 4: COMPUTE Yi SCORE]
  M3b --> M4

  M4 --> M4a[For each provider i:<br/>Yi = Σ V(benefit) - Σ V(cost)]
  M4 --> M4b[Benefit criteria (+):<br/>KandunganNutrisi<br/>Kualitas<br/>Dampak<br/>RamahLingkungan<br/>Ketersediaan]
  M4 --> M4c[Cost criteria (-):<br/>Harga]

  M4a --> M5[🏆 STEP 5: RANKING]
  M4b --> M5
  M4c --> M5

  M5 --> M5a[Sort by Yi score descending]
  M5 --> M5b[Rank 1 = highest Yi]
  M5 --> M5c[Compute percentile (0-100)]
  M5 --> M5d[Identify strengths:<br/>provider with max in criterion]
  M5 --> M5e[Identify weaknesses:<br/>provider with min in criterion]

  M5a --> OUT[📤 OUTPUT]
  M5b --> OUT
  M5c --> OUT
  M5d --> OUT
  M5e --> OUT

  OUT --> O1[Ranked Provider List<br/>with Yi scores]
  OUT --> O2[Normalized Matrix Table<br/>Nij values]
  OUT --> O3[Weighted Score Table<br/>Vij values]
  OUT --> O4[Winner Crown Badge<br/>Rank 1 provider]
  OUT --> O5[Strength / Weakness Tags<br/>per provider]

  O1 --> SAVE[💾 SAVE TO DATABASE]

  SAVE --> SA1[Create Comparison record<br/>prisma.comparison.create]
  SA1 --> SA2[Store providerIds + winner<br/>+ full results JSON]
  SA2 --> SA3[Create Audit Log entry<br/>action: COMPARISON<br/>entity: comparison]
  SA3 --> E([END])
